<ul data-start="206" data-end="541">
<li data-start="206" data-end="282">
<p data-start="208" data-end="282"><strong data-start="208" data-end="223">Card Points</strong>: Currency earned through progression used to unlock stars.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="283" data-end="370">
<p data-start="285" data-end="370"><strong data-start="285" data-end="294">Nodes</strong>: Each star (major or minor) is a <code data-start="328" data-end="334">Node</code> with unlock conditions and bonuses.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="371" data-end="446">
<p data-start="373" data-end="446"><strong data-start="373" data-end="382">Edges</strong>: Lines connecting stars (optional for visual/path constraints).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="447" data-end="541">
<p data-start="449" data-end="541"><strong data-start="449" data-end="464">Player Path</strong>: Players trace/select intended path and commit once they have enough points.</p>
</li>
</ul>
